.SH NAME
specscan \- extract individual scans from a file generated by SPEC
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B specscan
.RI [ options ] \ scan#1 \ scan#2 ... \ scan#N \ SPEC_file
.\".br
.\".B bar
.\".RI [ options ] "files" ...
